title: 11/27/2020 – Hour 1 – Lamar Jackson or Kyler Murray? Plus, Tyler Dunne!
itunes:title: 11/27/2020 – Hour 1 – Lamar Jackson or Kyler Murray? Plus, Tyler Dunne!
description:
Jason McIntyre and Rob Parker talk about the putrid slate of NFL games on Thanksgiving and weigh in on the NFL’s plan to go through with the Ravens / Steelers match-up despite numerous positive tests coming out of Baltimore. The guys debate which quarterback they would rather having going forward; Lamar Jackson or Kyler Murray. Plus they speak with Tyler Dunne, founder of ‘Go Long’, about the biggest NFL headlines.
